іца)</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-bg"><a href="https://bg.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B0%D1%82%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BA_%D0%A3%D0%B0%D0%B9%D1%82" title="Патрик Уайт — bulgare" lang="bg" hreflang="bg" class="interlanguage-link-target">Български</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-br"><a href="https://br.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_White" title="Patrick White — breton" lang="br" hreflang="br" class="interlanguage-link-target">Brezhoneg</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ca"><a href="https://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_White" title="Patrick White — catalan" lang="ca" hreflang="ca" class="interlanguage-link-target">Català</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-cs"><a href="https://cs.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_White" title="Patrick White — tchèque" lang="cs" hreflang="cs" class="interlanguage-link-target">Čeština</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-cy"><a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_White" title="Patrick White — gallois" lang="cy" hreflang="cy" class="interlanguage-link-target">Cymraeg</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-da"><a href="https://da.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_White" title="Patrick White — danois" lang="da" hreflang="da" class="interlanguage-link-target">Dansk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-de"><a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_White" title="Patrick White — allemand" lang="de" hreflang="de" class="interlanguage-link-target">Deutsch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-el"><a href="https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%A0%CE%AC%CF%84%CF%81%CE%B9%CE%BA_%CE%93%CE%BF%CF%85%CE%AC%CE%B9%CF%84" title="Πάτρικ Γουάιτ — grec" lang="el" hreflang="el" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ελληνικά</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-en"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_White" title="Patrick White — anglais" lang="en" hreflang="en" class="interlanguage-link-target">English</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-eo"><a 