<li><span class="wd_identifiers">Notices dans des dictionnaires ou encyclopédies généralistes<span class="noprint wikidata-linkback"><a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q129187?uselang=fr#identifiers" title="Voir et modifier les données sur Wikidata"><img alt="Voir et modifier les données sur Wikidata" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/10px-Blue_pencil.svg.png" decoding="async" width="10" height="10" style="vertical-align: baseline" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/15px-Blue_pencil.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/20px-Blue_pencil.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600" /></a></span></span>&#160;: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://adb.anu.edu.au/biography/white-patrick-victor-14925"><i>Australian Dictionary of Biography</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://brockhaus.de/ecs/enzy/article/white-patrick-victor-martindale"><i>Brockhaus Enzyklopädie</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.deutsche-biographie.de/118767607.html"><i>Deutsche Biographie</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.britannica.com/biography/Patrick-White"><i>Encyclopædia Britannica</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.universalis.fr/encyclopedie/patrick-white/"><i>Encyclopædia Universalis</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.enciclopedia.cat/EC-GEC-0072121.xml"><i>Gran Enciclopèdia Catalana</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=66083"><i>Hrvatska Enciklopedija</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ne.se/uppslagsverk/encyklopedi/lång/patrick-white"><i>Swedish Nationalencyklopedin</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://w